---
import MicroBlogLayout from '../../layouts/MicroBlogLayout.astro';
---

<MicroBlogLayout title="Getting Started with the PiaShare API">
	<article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
		<header class="mb-8">
			<h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
				Getting Started with the PiaShare API
			</h1>
			
			<div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">
				<span>Sarah Chen</span>
				<span>Dec 15, 2024</span>
				<span>5 min read</span>
			</div>

			<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
				<span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-base font-medium bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 dark:bg-blue-900 dark:text-blue-200">API</span>
				<span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-base font-medium bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 dark:bg-blue-900 dark:text-blue-200">Tutorial</span>
				<span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-base font-medium bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 dark:bg-blue-900 dark:text-blue-200">Getting Started</span>
			</div>
		</header>

		<div class="mb-8">
			<img 
				src="https://via.placeholder.com/800x400" 
				alt="Getting Started with PiaShare API" 
				class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-lg"
			/>
		</div>

		<div class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
			<p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
				Learn how to integrate PiaShare's powerful API into your applications with our comprehensive guide and examples.
			</p>

			<h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Prerequisites</h2>
			<p class="text-lg sm:text-xl mb-6 leading-relaxed">Before you start, make sure you have:</p>
			<ul class="list-disc pl-8 mb-8 text-lg sm:text-xl space-y-2">
				<li>A PiaShare developer account</li>
				<li>Basic knowledge of REST APIs</li>
				<li>Your preferred programming language</li>
			</ul>

			<h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Authentication</h2>
			<p class="text-lg sm:text-xl mb-6 leading-relaxed">PiaShare API uses API keys for authentication:</p>

			<pre class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8 text-base sm:text-lg overflow-x-auto"><code>curl -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY" https://api.piashare.com/v1/user/profile</code></pre>

			<h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Basic Endpoints</h2>
			
			<h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Get User Profile</h3>
			<pre class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg mb-6 text-base sm:text-lg overflow-x-auto"><code>GET https://api.piashare.com/v1/user/profile</code></pre>

			<h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Create a New Project</h3>
			<pre class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg mb-4 text-base sm:text-lg overflow-x-auto"><code>POST https://api.piashare.com/v1/projects</code></pre>
			<pre class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8 text-base sm:text-lg overflow-x-auto"><code>Content-Type: application/json

&#123;
  "name": "My Project",
  "description": "Sample project"
&#125;</code></pre>

			<h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Next Steps</h2>
			<p class="text-lg sm:text-xl mb-6 leading-relaxed">Now you can:</p>
			<ul class="list-disc pl-8 mb-8 text-lg sm:text-xl space-y-2">
				<li>Explore the full API documentation</li>
				<li>Check out our SDK libraries</li>
				<li>Join our developer community</li>
			</ul>

			<p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-medium">Happy coding! üöÄ</p>
		</div>

		<div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
			<a href="/" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">‚Üê Back to all posts</a>
		</div>
	</article>
</MicroBlogLayout>